ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I think anyone who wants to read Arabic should take this class from Michael Rapoport.
Yes, it was both a didactic class and a place to have fun and enjoy.
I would highly, highly recommend this course for any student at all serious about furthering their knowledge of Arabic.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I learned so much in a single semester; much more than I have learned in years.
N/A. The course will not be a tool for me for future studies.
